Classes in de.javasoft.swing.filter that implement IRowFilterModel
 class AbstractRowFilterModel<M>
          AbstractRowFilterModel is an abstract base implemenation of IRowFilterModel which handles listeners and their notification.
 class ComparableRowFilterModel<M>
          ComparableRowFilterModel is a concrete implementation of RowFilterModel for creating RowFilters for values of type Comparable.
 class PatternRowFilterModel<M>
          A pattern matching implementation of RowFilterModel.
 class SimpleRowFilterModel<M>
